@{b} Introduction @{ub}


UpRC  is an utility  for easy creating Aminet upload readme
files.  There are some tools available doing this job.  But
none of them are really useable in my mind and provide  all
features of the Aminet readmes.

This program is  heavily  under construction,  so  you  may
request some extensions, changes or bugfixes to @{"me" link author}.

There is an example  @{"TREE" link upload}  file  to show  you the type and
format of one of them  to possibly update the internal UpRC
UpRC types list by yourself.

UpRC is FreeWare again.

@Endnode
@Node requirements "UpRC"
@Next installation
@Prev introduction
@Toc main

@{b} Requirements @{ub}


* OS 3.0+ - Good to have it :)
* aminetrd.library 23.0+ (included in this package)
* @{"textfield.gadget" link textfield} (included in this package)
* enough free memory (min 2M)

@Endnode
