        - Change: "Edit - Required"    page    renamed   to
                  "Recommended".
        - Change: "Distribution:"     entry     moved    to
                  "Edit - Additional" page.
        - Change: Class selecting button removed.
        - Change: Layout   of   text   displaying   gadgets
