        - Bug:    Textfield handling bug removed.
        - Change: Restoring settings  and  upload types now
                  works fine.
        - Change: Distribution  field  of  readme files now
                  supported.
        - Change: Gadget shortcuts removed.  There is a bug
                  in the GUI engine!
        - Bug:    Reading    readme    files    bug   (long
